extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em LocalGrocery], a very basic Express website developed as an example on the Mozilla Developer Network.

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The grocery has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Products:] !{data.product_count}
      li #[strong Copies available:] !{data.book_instance_available_count} 
      li #[strong Clients:] !{data.client_count}
    